    I'm back!  I'm in...somewhat a normal place.  Washington State!  I've 
exited Alaska.  I'm at my computer and -- WHAT THE HELL!?  1000 e-mails!?
    Who the hell do you think I am, Jesus Christ?  Well...don't tell 
anyone...but...

    You may think I have fully returned...but unfortunately, that is new 
true.  I was going to read the e-mails...but 1000...I'm just going to get 
info from the other Council members.  The Events page...I was hoping Yanshosh 
would take care of it, but that isn't the case.  So, that won't be updated 
for the days I was gone.  Sorry.  

    I plan on being back in da game tomorrow after having a nice long chat 
with Yanshosh.  My dad and brother will be gone, so Junior Czar Unitron (me), 
will have ze whole house to himself.  

    So, if you've got any formal complaints with me, no offense intended, but 
it's midnight, I'm kind of tired, "Unhappily Everafter" is coming on, so you 
can shove 'em.


Lord Unitron
"Working for a better tomorrow, for himself."
